# hero-skulth — APPS concern (SECRET class by suffix; radius: apps)
# Copy to .env.apps at the repo root; the seal keeps it out of history.

# skulþ data-plane consumer pair — SAME values as skulþ's .env.apps holds
# (skulþ verifies, the pod presents). Minted 2026-07-20, registered.
SKULTH_API_KEY_POD=
SKULTH_API_SECRET_POD=

# NOTE — no wallet key line, by design (custody ruling b, skulth#4
# 2026-07-20): the pod mints its own wallet at first breath; the private
# key lives only in the sealed state dir (0600) and no human ever holds
# it. Rotation = a new life. The kill switch is also key destruction.
